{"tid":2041000,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公安部：指導港警止暴制亂 以黨監警 倡忠廉","createTime":"2020-05-29T03:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T03:43:15.000Z","uid":21470,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a32caad3ac29427016f4e64625da4d69bd7dc10d","tid":2041000,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:05:57.000Z","msg":"公安部：全力指導支持香港警隊止暴制亂<br />\n29.05.2020 08:12<br />\n<br />\n國務委員、公安部部長趙克志昨日主持召開公安部黨委擴大會議。會議指，全國人大昨日作出有關「港區國安法」的決定，意義重大而深遠，要認真學習貫徹，及全力指導支持香港警隊止暴制亂、恢復秩序，堅決維護香港安全穩定。<br />\n<br />\n會議又指出，要嚴密防範、嚴厲打擊境內外敵對勢力滲透顛覆搗亂破壞活動，堅決捍衛國家政治安全；要統籌推進各項公安改革任務，堅定不移走改革強警之路，著力健全制度、完善機制、提升能力，及毫不動搖抓好全面從嚴管黨治警，聚焦忠誠乾淨擔當，著力提高公安隊伍革命化正規化專業化職業化建設水平。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1293179&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1293179%26csid%3D261_341&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33HaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=d421d08a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1293179&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"24e99dc0a4372c73e313e6582839a8d361ea3d67","tid":2041000,"uid":74622,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:07:11.000Z","msg":"毅進仔學普通話會唔會有障礙?"},{"pid":"f80e978524cba7f1231e9c9fe032adea9ccacfd8","tid":2041000,"uid":145273,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:08:56.000Z","msg":"唔知點解倡忠廉依句野係佢地口中出覺得好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e4999bb8942ab9e239a45a7cfc97c0faea1cd7","tid":2041000,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T03:09:27.000Z","msg":"警察國家"},{"pid":"11c590741197112d4e543d7e8d5